narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: The Senior Essay can be a wonderful experience if youre motivated to do a lot of reading and writing on your own. It helps to come into the semester with a clear idea of what literature youll read and a general idea of the area that youll write about. I highly recommend this course to anyone who has a real desire to see what its like to do real philosophical work, especially if youre considering graduate study in philosophy.
